#

Lemon Garlic Shrimp with Zucchini Noodles

20 min
$12
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Shellfish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-CarbKeto

Cuisine:

Mediterranean

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

QuickHealthyLight

Description

A light and flavorful dish featuring succulent shrimp and fresh zucchini noodles tossed in a zesty lemon garlic sauce.

Ingredients

  • shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 pound
  • zucchini (spiralized): 2 medium
  • garlic (minced): 4 cloves
  • lemon (juiced and zested): 1
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • red pepper flakes (optional): 1/2 teaspoon
  • fresh parsley (chopped, for garnish): 2 tablespoons
